Post, Mar 24, 2012  Putouts: 1, 7 times Assists: 5, at C.W. Post, Mar 24, 2012  Runners CS: 2, CW Post, 03/31/11 CAREER HIGHS Personal: Born September 4, 1991 ... Daughter of Bob and Sue Thomas ... Has a brother Matt and sister Kate ... Sister Kate played softball at Bryant University. Before Merrimack: Played basketball and softball at Trinity High School ... Played four years of varsity softball at pitcher, outfield and infield under head coach Steve Gadecki ... Helped Trinity to their first playoff berth in four years as a senior ... Was a member of Pat Smith's varsity basketball team that made it to the state championship in her senior season ... Played on the New Hampshire Comets club softball team ... A member of the National Honor Society, Student Council and Campus Ministry.
